		Sunshield Chemicals Limited
		


		Apr 02, 2014
			









Sunshield Chemicals Limited (SCL) (CIN: L99999MH1986PLC041612) is related to Solvay’s Novecare business. SCL was acquired in the year 2012-13. SCL manufactures process chemicals that are formulated to meet requirements of industries and are known as “Specialty Chemicals” (SC). Specialty Chemicals manufactured by the Company find extensive use in diverse range of Industries such as Wire Insulation Enamel, PVC stabilizers, Inks, Colours, Coatings, Textiles, Agro-chemicals, Plastics, Rubber and Latex, Tyre and Tubes, Lubricant and additives, and many more.



The manufacturing site, located in Rasal (Maharashtra) is located 100 km south-east of Mumbai of Mumbai and employs about 94 people. 




Registered Office
Phoenix House, A Wing, 4th floor,
462, Senpati Bapat Marg, Lower Parel (West),
Mumbai - 400 013




Manufacturing
Pali-Khopoli Road, Village Rasal, Wave
Taluka Sudhagad,
Dist. Raigad, 
Maharashtra, India





































































