                    About us



Welcome To Our Site!


Sunshield Chemicals Limited is part of Solvay SA, Belgium. Sunshield is a leading manufacturer and exporter of Surfactants and Anti Oxidants.  Started as domestic player, Sunshield today serves a reputed clientele spread over America, Europe, South East Asia, Far East and Middle East.  Click for details>> 


